What is Subjugator?

MIL’s SubjuGator is the three-time champion autonomous submarine of the Robosub AUVSI/ONR underwater competition.

Awards

We have placed in the top 3 in eleven of the 21 years of the competition, including second place in 2012, 2013, and 2014.
